        <h4>The Problem</h4>
        <p>Iora Health is a radical new model for providing healthcare. The Iora team has redefined Primary Care as a new system to help patients receive better care and more optimally manage their health. To support this new system, where traditional pen and paper fall short, and current software solutions fit the old healthcare model, Iora Health needed a completely custom software stack to meet their innovative new process.</p>
        <p>The Iora Health team came to thoughtbot for an internal software solution that was designed to be custom tailored for their new healthcare model.</p>
      </section>
