        <h4>The Solution</h4>
        <p>We started our engagement with Iora Health by deep-diving into their new model to gather an exhaustive understanding of the process, requirements, and how
technology can help assist them in providing the most innovative health care
solutions possible.</p>
        <p>Working with Iora Health, we designed a transformative medical records system,
where all patient records are managed electronically and updated on-the-fly
for instantaneous communication between Iora's internal team of health care
specialists.</p>
        <p>The software was designed to be used on desktop computers as well as mobile tablets so that health care workers could use iPads while working directly with patients to update medical records, take notes, and generate tasks for coworkers and doctors. The combination of an iPad married with clear and meaningful software UX design, we were able to achieve a significant breakthrough in effectiveness and transparency of patient-doctor visits.</p>
